short_summary: Construction tender for new guard observation posts at Canadian Embassy in Haiti
description: His Majesty the King in right of Canada, represented by the Department of Foreign Affairs, Trade and Development (DFATD) requires the design and construction for new guard observation posts and patrol pathways for enhanced security.
